### ApplicationCatalogs V2 API

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@tenantId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
@username = admin
@password = P@ssw0rd!

### 登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/token
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

###
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.$.data.accessToken}}

### 查询目录列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/application-catalogs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 按状态/分类/AppKey筛选目录列表
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/application-catalogs?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&status=Published&category=workflow&appKey=demo
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 查询目录详情
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/application-catalogs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 修改目录数据源（仅未绑定目录可修改）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/application-catalogs/1/datasource
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "dataSourceId": "1"
}

### 编辑目录信息
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/application-catalogs/1
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "E2E Workspace App",
  "description": "更新后的目录描述",
  "category": "E2E",
  "icon": "appstore"
}

### 发布目录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v2/application-catalogs/1/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "releaseNote": "发布目录版本"
}
